{"type":null,"faqId":38521,"title":"设置帐户","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_task_add_account-chtext\"><span>1.</span><span> 添加帐户</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125574\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“添加帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>选择一个帐户类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>根据屏幕提示输入帐户相关信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.</span><a name=\"_task_remove_account-chtext\"><span> </span><span>删除帐户</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125575\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“帐户”界面，选择一个帐户类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>选择要删除的帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>按照界面的提示，删除帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.</span><a name=\"_task_start_sync-chtext\"><span> </span><span>开启电子邮件同步功能</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125576\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125577\" style=\"width:0.25694445in;height:0.18333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”,勾选“自动同步数据”，根据屏幕提示点击，开启同步数据开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“帐户”界面，选择一个帐户类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>选择要开启同步的帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“同步电子邮件”开关，开启帐户同步功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3801","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448687000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":130,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"设置帐户","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}